@startuml C2_Contenedores
!theme plain
title C2 — Diagrama de Contenedores\nSistema de Inventario DCRM

skinparam backgroundColor #1e293b
skinparam defaultFontColor #f1f5f9
skinparam componentBorderColor #6366f1

actor "Operador" as Op #6366f1
actor "Administrador" as Ad #ef4444

package "Sistema de Inventario DCRM" {

  component "Navegador Web\n[HTML5 + Bootstrap 5 Local\n+ JavaScript Vanilla\n+ Chart.js]" as Frontend #334155

  component "Aplicación Django\n[Python 3.11 / Django 5]\nPatrón MVT\nContenedor: dcrm/" as Backend #1e40af

  component "Motor de Plantillas\n[Django Templates\n+ Jinja2-like syntax]" as Templates #0f4c81

  database "MySQL 8.0\n[Base de Datos]\nBase: inventario_db" as MySQL #1a2e44

  component "Archivos Estáticos\n[Bootstrap CSS/JS local\ncustom.css]" as Static #374151

}

Op --> Frontend : Usa navegador
Ad --> Frontend : Usa navegador
Frontend --> Backend : HTTP Requests\nPOST (CSRF protegido)\nGET
Backend --> Templates : Renderiza HTML
Templates --> Frontend : HTML dinámico
Backend --> MySQL : ORM Django\n(mysqlclient)
Frontend --> Static : Carga Bootstrap\nCSS y JS locales

note right of Backend
  Capas de seguridad:
  1. Sesiones y cookies
  2. @login_required + roles
  3. Validación Regex
  4. Headers HTTP seguros
end note

@enduml
